can_subscribe.description: Indicates whether you can subscribe to this plan.

currency.description: The monetary unit in which pricing information is displayed.

externally_managed.description: Indicates whether this plan is managed externally.

frequency.description: The frequency at which you will be billed for this plan.

is_subscribed.description: Indicates whether you are currently subscribed to this plan.

legacy_discount.description: Indicates whether this plan has a legacy discount applied.

legacy_id.description: The legacy identifier for this rate plan, if any.

price.description: The amount you will be billed for this plan.
